{"tid":1828479,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國於南海有主權爭議地帶赤瓜礁 建解放軍基地豎立「祖國萬歲」標語","createTime":"2020-01-18T01:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T02:23:25.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75942481e72ac34aea4a58c6538260369ee9de94","tid":1828479,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/D9_DDv_eB8Wb4W48MGpkCSM0VN0=/760x505/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/CARZTWOUOON7JZMW5SJ2DTD6IE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FD9_DDv_eB8Wb4W48MGpkCSM0VN0%3D%2F760x505%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FCARZTWOUOON7JZMW5SJ2DTD6IE.jpg&h=4e30b581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝越南《青年報》<br />\n中國在習近平上台後，積極在南海擴展霸權，不但到處填島造陸，更把多個島嶼軍事化，導致中國與越南、澳洲等周邊國家的關係日益緊張。越南《青年報》（Thanh Ni&ecirc;n）周四（16日）發現，中國於「與越南有主權爭議」的赤瓜礁上，大興土木，島上不但有樓高26~27公尺的解放軍建築，建築物上還豎立「祖國萬歲」的標語。赤瓜礁是南沙群島九章群礁中的一個暗礁，中華民國將它劃歸在高雄市旗津區。<br />\n <br />\n《青年報》的記者，本月上旬前往赤瓜礁海域近距離拍攝，發現中國已在島上蓋了基地，不但有燈塔、電力設備，及兩組大型的風力發電機，還有大型軍事建築，包括：火炮、兩組空對空雷達塔、高50公尺的4G傳輸電信塔。<br />\n <br />\n報導又指，島上建有一個33平方公尺的直升機停機坪及一個碼頭，島上馬路寬約20至30公尺，可以停放運輸船上的卡車。而最顯眼的主建築，則被豎立上「祖國萬歲」的標語。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200118/Q6B3V2RTC4LV2VZB6JFC6WSI4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200118%2FQ6B3V2RTC4LV2VZB6JFC6WSI4I%2F&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKJBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=80f8bb40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200118%2FQ6B3V2RTC4LV2VZB6JFC6WSI4I%2F&h=a61697df\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200118/Q6B3V2RTC4LV2VZB6JFC6WSI4I/</a>"},{"pid":"c6985aaca537f51c1240eae11e92a55cf76c3bcf","tid":1828479,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:12:54.000Z","msg":"搞南海有撚用咩"},{"pid":"fb78606b17ea7ece3ce96873a9de3ec623f29c1f","tid":1828479,"uid":93649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:14:06.000Z","msg":"印度呀星都唔夠膽搞"},{"pid":"5f7eb5b91177792f7cd13d24de458eec3fb9d76e","tid":1828479,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb78606b17ea7ece3ce96873a9de3ec623f29c1f","tid":1828479,"uid":93649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:14:06.000Z","msg":"印度呀星都唔夠膽搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae162c0f8605d85f12d745a426d4e0596110669d","tid":1828479,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:23:25.000Z","msg":"之前印尼出戰機趕<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓出 F/A 50 投彈"}]}